Package com.snamp.hosting

Represents SNAMP Engine classes, heart of the SNAMP platform.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Agent.InstantiatedConnectors
    Represents a map of instantiated management connector.
    AgentConfiguration
    Represents in-memory representation of the agent configuration.
    AgentConfiguration.HostingConfiguration
    Represents hosting configuration (front-end configuration).
    AgentConfiguration.ManagementTargetConfiguration
    Represents management target configuration (back-end management information providers).
    AgentConfiguration.ManagementTargetConfiguration.AttributeConfiguration
    Represents attribute configuration.
    AgentConfiguration.ManagementTargetConfiguration.EventConfiguration
    Represents event configuration.
    AgentConfigurationStorage
    Represents a storage for AgentConfiguration instance.
    AgentConfigurationStorage.StoredAgentConfiguration
    Represents persisted agent configuration.
    HostingContext
    Represents agent hosting context and describes SNAMP environment at runtime.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractAgentConfiguration
    Represents a base class for custom agent configuration holders.
    Agent
    Represents SNAMP hosting agent that provides interoperability between adapter and connectors.
    EmbeddedAgentConfiguration
    Represents embedded agent configuration.
    EmbeddedAgentConfiguration.EmbeddedHostingConfiguration
    Represents adapter settings.
    EmbeddedAgentConfiguration.EmbeddedManagementTargetConfiguration
    Represents configuration of the management information provider.
    EmbeddedAgentConfiguration.EmbeddedManagementTargetConfiguration.EmbeddedAttributeConfiguration
    Represents configuration of the management attribute.
    EmbeddedAgentConfiguration.EmbeddedManagementTargetConfiguration.EmbeddedEventConfiguration
    Represents configuration of the event source.
  • Enum Summary

    ConfigurationFormat
    Represents configuration file parser.

Package com.snamp.hosting Description

Represents SNAMP Engine classes, heart of the SNAMP platform.

This package contains SNAMP Engine that organizes interoperability between SNAMP connectors and adapters.

See Also:
Agent, AgentConfiguration
